Frank Wilcox https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frank_Wilcox 0 Frank Reppy Wilcox (March 13, 1907 – March 3, 1974) was an American character actor who made appearances in more than 150 films and nearly 200 episodes of television programs.
